<h2 id="the-payoff">The Payoff</h2>

<p>If you go to <a href="/blog/random">derekkedziora.com/blog/random</a>, youâ€™ll automatically be redirected to a random post on my blog.</p>

<p>For a more philosophical read about randomness, thereâ€™s always <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Dice_Man">The Dice Man</a>. Have some fun and get outside your bubble with randomness.</p>

